OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,FA woman from has been sharing her
OL,7,Fordeal of being in pain for almost a
OL,8,Fdecade waiting for a hip replacement,
OL,9,Fonly to be forced to wait even longer
OL,10,Ffor surgery due to an error by the
OL,11,Fhealth board.
OL,13,FJoanne Dix, 49, says the mistake in
OL,14,Fcancelling a pre-planned operation by
OL,15,Fthe health board has left her living
OL,16,Fwith bouts of depression and wanting
OL,17,Fget her pain-free life back.
OL,19,FJoanne was first referred to hospital
OL,20,Fin 2018 for pain in her right hip and
OL,21,Fthen again in 2021 for her left.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/20
