OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,FIt was found that the referral for her
OL,7,Fleft hip was closed in error, however
OL,8,Fin 2023 her left hip was treated. She
OL,9,Fwas then removed from the waiting list
OL,10,Ffor her right hip, even though this
OL,11,Fstill required treatment.
OL,13,FJoanne's first hip-related appointment
OL,14,Fwas almost eight years ago, meaning
OL,15,Fshe's been in constant pain throughout
OL,16,Fthat period.
