OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"It's difficult, it impacts on daily
OL,7,Flife, just basic things. I found a lot
OL,8,Fof impact through covid when I just
OL,9,Fwanted to go walking and you just
OL,10,Fcan't go walking unless you dose up on
OL,11,Fso much pain relief.
OL,13,F"You push through it but then for the
OL,14,Fnext week you're struggling to get in
OL,15,Fand out of bed or up and down off the
OL,16,Fsofa and it's just impacted on every
OL,17,Faspect of daily living
