OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"I went through a bout of depression.
OL,7,FDoing a lot of sports and then being
OL,8,Ftold you can't do as much with the
OL,9,Fkids or the family. Having to turn
OL,10,Fthings down, people going for coastal
OL,11,Fwalks, things like that and having to
OL,12,Fthink if you can do it.
