OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"You build your hopes up. You know
OL,7,Fthat pre-assessment lasts for six
OL,8,Fmonths, so you're expecting to go in
OL,9,Fat that timeframe and then nothing
OL,10,Fhappens and you get called for another
OL,11,Fone and you wait again for another six
OL,12,Fmonths and then you get called for
OL,13,Fanother one and you wait again for
OL,14,Fanother six months and then you get
OL,15,Fcalled for a third one and then you
OL,16,Ffind out in the report that was an
OL,17,Ferror.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/20
