OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"So then it becomes upsetting that
OL,7,Fit's unnecessary cost on the NHS,
OL,8,Fgetting you in for pre-assessments
OL,9,Fwhich are not required or made in
OL,10,Ferror and you're not having the
OL,11,Fsurgery either.
OL,13,F'How many other people is it happening
OL,14,Fto?'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/20
