OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,FShe says her ordeal has really taken
OL,7,Fits toll on her family, her marriage
OL,8,Fand her work life: "I was angry, I was
OL,9,Ffrustrated, I was in pain, not
OL,10,Fsleeping, so then I was tired and just
OL,11,Fgenerally everything getting on top of
OL,12,Fme.
OL,14,FJoanne has said she doesn't blame the
OL,15,Fdoctors or clinicians who she's dealt
OL,16,Fwith already but the NHS management
OL,17,Fwho have mishandled the situation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/20
