OL,11,F"If this has happened to me, how many
OL,12,Fother people is it happening to? If I
OL,13,Fhadn't gone to the Ombudsman would
OL,14,Fthese failings have been recognised?"
OL,16,F"I just want the surgery, I just want
OL,17,Fto be out of pain, I just want to get
OL,18,Fmy daily living back before I hit my
OL,19,F50s really and start living life pain-
OL,20,Ffree.
