OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,FJoanne's experience isn't one simply
OL,7,Fconfined to her, with other patients
OL,8,Falso having to wait significant
OL,9,Fperiods for orthopaedic surgery in the
OL,10,FSwansea Bay area.
OL,12,FTwo other complainants, who have
OL,13,Fchosen to remain anonymous, have also
OL,14,Ftaken their cases to the ombudsman
OL,15,Fafter being in similar situations to
OL,16,FJoanne.
OL,18,FIn the case of "Mr C", he had been
OL,19,Fassessed as needing surgery within a
OL,20,Fmonth but waited three years seven
OL,21,Fmonths whilst in severe pain.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/20
