OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"These 3 cases demonstrate clear
OL,7,Finjustice to the patients.
OL,9,F"In addition to these failings, the
OL,10,Fcomplainants had the unnecessary
OL,11,Fstress and pain of pre-operative
OL,12,Fassessments. I am concerned that there
OL,13,Fappears to have been no thought for
OL,14,Fthe impact of these on the patients'
OL,15,Fwellbeing.
OL,17,FThe Ombudsman has made the following
OL,18,Frecommendations of which the health
OL,19,Fboard has agreed to implement.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/20
