OL,6,FIn response to the report, for the
OL,7,Ffailings in how their appointments
OL,8,Fwere managed.
OL,10,F"We have accepted the Ombudsman's
OL,11,Frecommendations in full and they will
OL,12,Fbe implemented over the next few weeks.
OL,14,F"We can confirm that all three
OL,15,Fpatients have now received their
OL,16,Foperations. We are checking our
OL,17,Forthopaedic waiting lists to ensure
OL,18,Fthere are no other similar cases, and
OL,19,Fif there are, we will again urgently
OL,20,Fexpedite their care.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/20
