OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"Along with scrutinising our
OL,7,Forthopaedic waiting lists, additional
OL,8,Fstaff training is in place to ensure
OL,9,Freferral to treatment time rules are
OL,10,Ffollowed.
OL,12,F"Our orthopaedic services are under
OL,13,Fhuge pressure, and we are doing all we
OL,14,Fcan to tackle waiting lists, including
OL,15,Flaunching the new orthopaedic theatre
OL,16,Fhub at Neath Port Talbot Hospital
OL,17,Fseven months ago.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/20
