OL,3,CWoman shares woes of cancelled hip
OL,4,Csurgery and enduring a decade of pain
OL,6,F"In most cases, the orthopaedic
OL,7,Fpatients who have waited the longest
OL,8,Fhave had other health concerns as
OL,9,Fwell, so needed their operation in
OL,10,FMorriston Hospital. Crucially we have
OL,11,Fnow re-established 10 ring-fenced beds
OL,12,Fin Morriston for this group of
OL,13,Fpatients with complex health needs.
OL,15,F"This action, together with the new
OL,16,Forthopaedic theatres in Neath Port
OL,17,FTalbot Hospital, means the longest
OL,18,Fwaiting times are now coming down.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/20
