OL,6,F"We anticipate that by the end of
OL,7,FMarch there will be no patients
OL,8,Fwaiting over three years for their
OL,9,Fsurgery, with the majority of
OL,10,Forthopaedic patients who do not have
OL,11,Fadditional health needs being seen
OL,12,Fsooner."
