OL,6,FIn response to Joanne's claim she had
OL,7,Fnot received treatment, Health Board
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are not able to discuss
OL,9,Findividual patient cases in detail,
OL,10,Fbut we can confirm that while all
OL,11,Fthree patients in the Ombudsman's
OL,12,Freports have received orthopaedic
OL,13,Fsurgery, in one case another
OL,14,Forthopaedic operation is now scheduled.
OL,16,F"We are in direct contact with this
OL,17,Fpatient, who is due to have their
OL,18,Fremaining surgery very shortly. We are
OL,19,Fhappy to discuss with the patient any
OL,20,Ffurther queries they may have."
